	(text_box "Note:\nSDRAM\n- CKE Clock Enable (LOW) can be put into a low power state To enter a deep sleep Issue a SELF REFRESH command  while CKE is pulled Low\n\nNAND\n- Use FMC_NCE CE Chip Enable (HIGH) to put into low power mode"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
