	(text "0.1µF (100nF) ceramic capacitor per VCC and VCCQ pin\nPlace 100nF capacitors as close as possible to each \npower pin to filter high-frequency noise.\nBulk Capacitor near one of the VCC pins (Pin 38 or Pin 48)."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
